OL,3,CRace-related disorder in NI cost
OL,4,Calmost #1.5m to police
OL,6,FAlmost #1.5m - that is how much it
OL,7,Fcost to police the first days of race-
OL,8,Frelated disorder on the streets of
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland.
OL,11,FAnd the bill is still rising with the
OL,12,FPSNI in mobilisation mode ` meaning
OL,13,Fthey remain ready to act should
OL,14,Ftrouble again flare up.
OL,16,F"One of the big things talked about
OL,17,Fearlier in the year was the police
OL,18,Fresponse to the amount of people being
OL,19,Fkilled or seriously injured on our
OL,20,Froads," says Liam Kelly from the
OL,21,FPolice Federation.
