OL,6,F"So could that money be used to put
OL,7,Fmore roads policing crews out?
OL,8,FAbsolutely."
OL,10,FProtests, sporadic rioting, the
OL,11,Ftargeting of homes and businesses in
OL,12,Fvarious locations across Belfast
OL,13,Fstretching police.
OL,15,FThe nine-day policing bill a snapshot
OL,16,Fbut an insight on top of an already
OL,17,Fwell-documented funding crisis.
OL,19,FAll areas impacted appear to have
OL,20,Freturned to normal but tensions remain.
