OL,6,FWhile we were filming one man on a
OL,7,Fbike shouted at us "they should go
OL,8,Fback to their own country".
OL,10,FBut many others very angry money has
OL,11,Fgone down the drain trying to keep
OL,12,Fpeople safe from those bent on causing
OL,13,Ftrouble on the streets
OL,15,F"It costs an awful lot of money to
OL,16,Fpolice," one man said.
