OL,6,F"But sure how are you going to recoup
OL,7,Fthat? You just can't. It's all
OL,8,Feducation, people need to be told that
OL,9,Feverybody can live, but that's not the
OL,10,Fway it goes here, is it?"
OL,12,FThe nine-day policing bill doesn't
OL,13,Fcover the cost of those extra 80
OL,14,Fofficers brought in from Scotland to
OL,15,Fhelp out here.
OL,17,FThey officially start duties tomorrow.
OL,19,FThe police budget already under huge
OL,20,Fstrain with most of it taken up with
OL,21,Fsalaries.
