OL,4,Calmost #1.5m to police
OL,6,FBack in July police received just #23
OL,7,Fmillion out of more than #300m
OL,8,Frequested in the June monitoring round.
OL,10,FChief Constable Jon Boutcher said
OL,11,Fpolicing here is in a "really tough
OL,12,Fplace" and lags behind the rest of the
OL,13,FUK in terms of budget increases.
OL,15,FMeanwhile, the crackdown against those
OL,16,Finvolved in the recent rioting,
OL,17,Fincluding that in Londonderry on
OL,18,FSaturday in the Bogside, continues.
OL,20,FThirty-nine people have so far been
OL,21,Farrested and 30 have been charged.
